    <item>
      <title>国际货币基金组织称波兰可能在 2025 年中期开始降息</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/imf-says-poland-may-start-gradual-interest-rate-cuts-in-mid-2025</link>
      <description><![CDATA[国际货币基金组织表示，波兰可能在明年年中开始逐步降息，但建议央行行长在 2025 年全年保持紧缩货币政策，因为通胀风险很大。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/imf-says-poland-may-start-gradual-interest-rate-cuts-in-mid-2025</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 12:07:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>瑞典将修改预算规则以允许增加公共支出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/sweden-to-change-budget-rules-to-allow-more-government-spending</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞典将放弃预算盈余目标，利用北欧国家的低债务水平来增加国防支出并恢复破旧的基础设施。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-17/sweden-to-change-budget-rules-to-allow-more-government-spending</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 17 Oct 2024 10:09:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
